{"tid":1010663,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"源自英國爆紅卡通《Peppa Pig》","createTime":"2019-02-06T06:53:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T12:24:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7dae4bd14ba624a08d6a9030df4301ddf8acb837","tid":1010663,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T06:53:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190206/20607371\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190206%2F20607371&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTPUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=788683cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190206%2F20607371&h=e768c5a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190206/20607371</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年02月06日 <br />\n<br />\n源自英國爆紅卡通《Peppa Pig》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190206/large/06cx50p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190206%2Flarge%2F06cx50p.jpg&h=967f05c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小豬佩奇在其卡通中，亦有賀年橋段。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n引發內地極大迴響的《啥是佩奇》，在農曆現年前夕如同病毒般刷爆微博和朋友圈，究竟啥是佩奇？原來這可愛的卡通小豬佩奇，源於英國，又名《粉紅豬小妹》，英文名為《Peppa Pig》，是歷年來最具潛力的學前兒童品牌之一，也是一部深受全球幼兒和家長喜愛的動畫片。在英國家長的眼中，小豬佩奇是當地生活理念的一個縮影。不過，小豬佩奇一家在中國曾被二次創作及惡搞，又與不務正業的年輕人畫上等號，官方去年出手封殺，事隔9個月才獲解禁及登上大銀幕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：港人回鄉陪八旬母過年彌補愧疚<br />\n<br />\n遭惡搞變低俗　官方封殺<br />\n<br />\n《小豬佩奇過大年》由中國阿里巴巴影業公司，與英國Entertainment One聯合出品的動畫電影，講述主人翁小豬佩奇與父母、弟弟及祖父母在除夕夜團聚，體驗中國傳統習俗的故事，動畫內將出現放煙花、舞龍等喜慶場面，還有吃湯圓及吃餃子南北等過年風俗，影片於年初一上映。<br />\n<br />\n這個人見人愛的粉紅豬家庭，早於2015年已和中國觀眾打交道，超過100集動畫被繙譯後在央視少兒頻道播出，成為家喻戶曉的人物。但該動畫去年5月遭影音平台「抖音」封殺，更被視為含有暴力、低俗、不雅等行為，並禁止播出。理由是有網民將小豬佩奇二次創作，加入惡搞元素，令內容變低俗，有網民更將卡通人物紋在身上，搖身一變成為所謂的「社會人」標誌，引起官方注意而遭封殺，《人民日報》曾發表評論，點名這齣動畫引發「跟風熱潮」需要警惕。  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n港人回鄉陪八旬母過年彌補愧疚<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n子女離家　農村長者精神空虛<br />\n<br />\n港人回鄉陪八旬母過年彌補愧疚<br />\n子女離家　農村長者精神空虛<br />\n兩岸專題：《啥是佩奇》揭空巢老人悲哀"},{"pid":"0e28ada2fe212225af1bd9e35ca6e775e1b4bc7a","tid":1010663,"uid":144,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T07:40:48.000Z","msg":"小豬社會人🤡"},{"pid":"c94a065ee3737514401833ebf5daa2dc6d901dc6","tid":1010663,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T07:42:33.000Z","msg":"小豬佩奇過大年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a7c573ef770346ecf0ba87188afbe7544f2b64","tid":1010663,"uid":75610,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T07:43:19.000Z","msg":"講野講野講野"},{"pid":"fc271b734b9725c7d4403515ec113c0ccf5be95f","tid":1010663,"uid":39181,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T11:23:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kqbyybB3XOE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkqbyybB3XOE&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTPUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=ea4851a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kqbyybB3XOE</a>"},{"pid":"681765c5d69cefb81db0557d90690840d5db5aca","tid":1010663,"uid":56661,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T12:07:12.000Z","msg":"總係覺得佢老豆塊面好似有毛嘅春袋"},{"pid":"c77a66629d4539601a07258425b91e6503853bf7","tid":1010663,"uid":31261,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T12:08:55.000Z","msg":"一直都覺得佢地有4隻眼"},{"pid":"4fc540b106afa4550175ed61b4639878b9335a35","tid":1010663,"uid":68944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc271b734b9725c7d4403515ec113c0ccf5be95f","tid":1010